    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections, while the interior remains in a pristine state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with the engine and transmission operating smoothly and all maintenance records up to date. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a car in showroom-quality condition with zero issues.",
